e VR meetings\n- Multi-user collaboration meetings have never been easier using access codes & passwords\n\nHave questions? Reach out to us at hello@sentiovr.com", "short_description": "Want to view a construction project before it's built? With SENTIO VR, multiple stakeholders in a project can meet virtually, voice-chat & collaborate over a 3D model enabling better decisions.\n\nSupports SketchUp, Revit & 360 panoramas.\n\nNeed some inspiration? Explore a unique collection of 360 experiences of architectural spaces curated by ArchDaily & our content team.\n\nNote: \n-Permission for Microphone is needed for VR meetings\n-Permission for Device files is needed for downloading 3D models"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://docs.google.com/document/d/1qFROWZPNG97M6dEBbC4k0YLRcanJt7Q98sCi56HR6MI/edit?usp=sharing", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "SENTIO VR", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://sentiovr.com/", "category": "APPS", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1063584910766706"}, {"id": "1819021644882647"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["PRODUCTIVITY"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER"], "id": "3013178319011693"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "279903826853759"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "279903826853759"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1615562580, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "279903826853759"}]}, "liveChannel": {"